snippet.title: Artillery Royale: Trailer Early Access
snippet.description:
Artillery Royale is multiplayer turn by turn Artillery game with fun physics, random maps, powerful spells and crazy weapons! 🧨 💥 😂
Get it on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1474410/Artillery_Royale/
